{"id":"5859acbf-19c1-a423-7a71-09f7c0845b01","Content":[{"Language":"nl-NL","Content":"[$BOX]\n\t[$CELL]\n\t\t[$BLOCK]\n\n\t\t\t<h3>7.10.3 Verlaten van de pati&euml;ntenkamer zonder ziektekiemen mee te nemen</h3>\n            <table class=\"table-excel-borders\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n                <tbody valign=\"top\" align=\"left\">\n                    <tr>\n                        <th width=\"50%\">Handeling: Verlaten van de pati&euml;ntenkamer zonder ziektekiemen mee te nemen</th>\n                        <th width=\"10%\">N.v.t</th>\n                        <th width=\"10%\">Goed</th>\n                        <th width=\"10%\">Kan beter</th>\n                        <th width=\"10%\">Fout</th>\n                        <th width=\"10%\">Niet gedaan</th>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"table-excel-oddrow\">\n                        <td><strong>1. Verzamelt de benodigdheden</strong></td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"table-excel-oddrow\">\n                        <td>1.1 Wasmand</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"table-excel-oddrow\">\n                        <td>1.2 Vuilniszak</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"table-excel-evenrow\">\n                        <td><strong>2. Hanteert adequaat de werkwijze:</strong></td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"table-excel-evenrow\">\n                        <td>2.1 Maakt de ceintuur van de overschort los.</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"table-excel-evenrow\">\n                        <td>2.2 Trekt de handschoenen uit door middel van de volgende stappen:</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"table-excel-evenrow\">\n                        <td>\n                            <ol style=\"list-style-type: lower-alpha;\">\n                                <li>Verwijdert de eerste handschoen door deze binnenstebuiten te keren.</li>\n                            </ol>\n                        </td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"table-excel-evenrow\">\n                        <td>\n                            <ol style=\"list-style-type: lower-alpha;\" start=\"2\">\n                                <li>Plaatst de opgerolde handschoen in de andere hand.</li>\n                            </ol>\n                        </td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"table-excel-evenrow\">\n                        <td>\n                            <ol style=\"list-style-type: lower-alpha;\" start=\"3\">\n                                <li>Verwijdert de andere handschoen door &eacute;&eacute;n vinger onder de rand van de handschoen te doen en de handschoen uit te trekken.</li>\n                            </ol>\n                        </td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"table-excel-evenrow\">\n                        <td>\n                            <ol style=\"list-style-type: lower-alpha;\" start=\"4\">\n                                <li>Gooit de handschoenen in de afvalzak.</li>\n                            </ol>\n                        </td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"table-excel-evenrow\">\n                        <td>2.3 Maakt het overschort los bij de hals.</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"table-excel-evenrow\">\n                        <td>2.4 Doet het overschort uit door deze van de schouders af te trekken.</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"table-excel-evenrow\">\n                        <td>2.5 Keert het schort binnenstebuiten en haalt de armen uit de mouwen.</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"table-excel-evenrow\">\n                        <td>2.6 Gooit het overschort in de wasmand.</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"table-excel-evenrow\">\n                        <td>Of</td>\n                        <td>&nbsp;</td>\n                        <td>&nbsp;</td>\n                        <td>&nbsp;</td>\n                        <td>&nbsp;</td>\n                        <td>&nbsp;</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"table-excel-evenrow\">\n                        <td>2.6 Gooit het wegwerpoverschort in de afvalzak.</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"table-excel-evenrow\">\n                        <td>2.7 Verwijdert de oogbeschermers.</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"table-excel-evenrow\">\n                        <td>2.8 Verwijdert het mond-neusmasker en gooit het in de afvalzak.</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"table-excel-evenrow\">\n                        <td>2.9 Wast de handen binnen de kamer.</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"table-excel-evenrow\">\n                        <td>2.10 Verlaat de kamer en wast/desinfecteert de handen bij de dichtstbijzijnde gootsteen.</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"table-excel-evenrow\">\n                        <td>2.11 Verwijdert alle voorwerpen die in de twee zakken zijn gedaan door deze naar de afvalkamer te brengen.</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"table-excel-evenrow\">\n                        <td>2.12 Brengt het wasgoed naar de juiste wasmand.</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"table-excel-evenrow\">\n                        <td>2.13 Voert handhygi&euml;ne uit.</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                        <td>□</td>\n                    </tr>\n                </tbody>\n            </table>\n\n\t\t[$/BLOCK]\n\t[$/CELL]\n[$/BOX]","Name":"7.10.3 Verlaten van de patiëntenkamer zonder ziektekiemen mee te nemen"}]}